    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo-的-NexT-教學"><a href="#Hexo-的-NexT-教學" class="headerlink" title="Hexo 的 NexT 教學"></a>Hexo 的 NexT 教學</h1><p>更換頭像、新增自介(about)、標籤(tags)與分類(categories) </p><h2 id="更換頭像"><a href="#更換頭像" class="headerlink" title="更換頭像"></a>更換頭像</h2><p>在<code>themes/NexT/_config.yml</code>裡找到頭像路徑<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/wzBBgiK.jpg" alt=""><br>可以直接更改圖片或是更改路徑指到圖片位置</p><h2 id="新增自我介紹-about"><a href="#新增自我介紹-about" class="headerlink" title="新增自我介紹( about )"></a>新增自我介紹( about )</h2><ol><li>進入 blog 下的 NexT設定檔開啟需要的功能<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim blog/themes/NexT/_config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://i.imgur.com/iuA0vd8.jpg" alt=""><br>找到 Menu 去掉註解來開啟想要的功能</li></ol><a id="more"></a><ol start="2"><li>新增 about 頁面</li></ol><p><code>hexo new page about</code></p><p>blog/source/ 下就會多一個 about 的資料夾<br>3. 更改 about/index.md 新增想要的內容</p><h2 id="新增標籤-tags"><a href="#新增標籤-tags" class="headerlink" title="新增標籤( tags )"></a>新增標籤( tags )</h2><ol><li>新增 標籤頁面<br><code>hexo new page tags</code> </li><li>進入新增的 tags/index.md 修改<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/BBUPCWk.jpg" alt=""><br>在第三行增加 type: “tags” </li></ol><h2 id="新增分類-categories"><a href="#新增分類-categories" class="headerlink" title="新增分類( categories )"></a>新增分類( categories )</h2><ol><li>新增 分類頁面<br><code>hexo new page categories</code> </li><li>進入新增的 categories/index.md  修改</li></ol><p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/ZzDARf8.jpg" alt=""></p><p>在第三行增加 type: “categories” </p><h2 id="使用標籤及分類"><a href="#使用標籤及分類" class="headerlink" title="使用標籤及分類"></a>使用標籤及分類</h2><p>正常的一篇文檔案開頭都會是</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: helloworld </span><br><span class="line">date:  2020-07-22017:17:09 </span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在 tags: 和 categories: 新增標籤及分類例如</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: helloworld </span><br><span class="line">date: 2020-07-22 17:17:09</span><br><span class="line">tags: </span><br><span class="line">    - pease </span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">    - Dad and Mom </span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如有多個標籤可以往下新增<br><font color = #ff00 >但分類則是有層級的比如</font></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">       title: helloworld </span><br><span class="line">       date: 2020-07-22 17:17:09</span><br><span class="line">       tags: </span><br><span class="line">           - Peace </span><br><span class="line">           - Love </span><br><span class="line">       categories:</span><br><span class="line">           - Dad and Mom </span><br><span class="line">           - Peter and Mike</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font color = #ff00>Peter and Mike 會是 Dad and Mom下的子分類</font></p><h2 id="參考連結"><a href="#參考連結" class="headerlink" title="參考連結"></a>參考連結</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/f138032e7539" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo next 主题配置右侧栏的分类和标签打开的是空白</a></li><li><a href="https://yogapan.github.io/2017/08/11/%E7%94%A8Hexo-Github-Pages%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">用Hexo + Github Pages搭建個人部落格</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
